==========================================================
Lesson 3: Blinking an LED
--------------------------
    Author: Chris Karaplis, info@simplyembedded.org
    Date: October 5, 2014
===========================================================

Description
------------
 - Create an infinite loop to blink LED1

Changelog
----------
 Added main.c

How to build
-------------
To build, execute the following command from the console in the project root directory:

    /opt/msp430-toolchain/bin/msp430-gcc -mmcu=msp430g2553 main.c

